Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,or incurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You reinforce the fact of it being incurable, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.34,0:01:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,However, some things cannot be altered, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,just because of the limitations of the linear domain.
