Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:01:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a reality of what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not just labeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
