Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, leaving the body, but reluctantly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Still giving one toehold on the physical body, yeah.
