Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, learn it completely,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and then after that, maybe the doorway will open for you to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,David likes the 21st Psalm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's too complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lord's Prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Start there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you get it down perfectly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to other prayer will open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:21:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:21:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do one, two, three?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's just say the Lord's Prayer right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how to say the Lord's Prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it's from this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll all do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.72,0:22:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In thy name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thy kingdom come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thy will be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,On earth as it is in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us this day our daily bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And forgive us as we forgive others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the test bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In his house he takes and delivers from his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The kingdom and the power and the glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:22:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:22:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.16,0:23:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to sign it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.06,0:23:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an attraction towards continuously surrendering, processing things out in a continuous fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,An attraction to constantly surrendering what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you're surrendering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I find that I'm often surrendering intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Like surrendering to the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just surrendering and allowing things to be, and in doing so, processing things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.19,0:24:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.69,0:24:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it seems as if I need to energize a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.49,0:24:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But that to do so is very dualistic from the surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.96,0:24:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.46,0:24:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting go of a thing doesn't require any mentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.96,0:24:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a willingness, a willingness to surrender it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.07,0:24:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.72,0:24:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the willingness to surrender, to allow to pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.31,0:24:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.24,0:24:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like there's an aversion towards praying separately from the surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.25,0:24:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Aversion towards praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.03,0:25:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As in, it seems like to energize a specific individual to pray, to say, oh Lord, please help me, seems to bring up a huge amount of aversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.43,0:25:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And that to do so would be actually abandoning the grace, which is supporting the surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.46,0:25:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.46,0:25:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.83,0:25:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.83,0:25:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.40,0:25:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All prayers do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.25,0:25:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how to let a thing go?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.07,0:25:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.07,0:25:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.07,0:25:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the essence of it, is really the willingness to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.69,0:25:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to control what happens after you let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.79,0:25:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You let it go, you let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.66,0:25:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't stay around to tailor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.66,0:25:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.83,0:26:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.83,0:26:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.83,0:26:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When you ask a prayer and.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.83,0:26:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said that it's called something, you have a name for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.83,0:26:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When you want this specifically to happen, you call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.83,0:26:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.83,0:26:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's, I'm not interested in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.83,0:26:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.83,0:26:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's an aversion towards praying, oh Lord, please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.06,0:26:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems as if that is pulling me away from just surrendering and allowing things to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.06,0:26:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then surrender without praying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.06,0:26:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.06,0:26:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.06,0:26:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.06,0:26:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just sometimes it seems like I have to cover both sides of the coin, if that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.06,0:26:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.06,0:26:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.06,0:26:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.06,0:26:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.06,0:26:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.06,0:26:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just making sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.06,0:26:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.06,0:26:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.06,0:26:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.06,0:26:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He goes, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.06,0:26:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to let it go and not let it go at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.06,0:26:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.06,0:26:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.06,0:27:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard for him to let it go and not let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.06,0:27:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.31,0:27:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.31,0:27:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to have a calibrated level of consciousness of around 600 to achieve a level of discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.31,0:27:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And also that we've all been programmed and we're all extremely gullible.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.64,0:27:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, what is it that I can trust within myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.64,0:27:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can trust that how you are asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.64,0:27:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.64,0:27:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How you are seeing and interpreting a thing is how you are seeing and interpreting a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.04,0:27:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you disappear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.92,0:27:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you disappear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.74,0:28:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because by naming it, you're disappearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.72,0:28:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And you ask God to reveal the essence and to remove the illusion of perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.83,0:28:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to see beyond perception to essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.48,0:28:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And you ask God's help to reveal it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.79,0:28:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part of the ritual of the Course in Miracles too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.50,0:28:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask to see beyond appearance to the essence of the reality behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.50,0:28:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.35,0:28:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the things you learn by doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.60,0:28:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It kind of becomes easier and easier, more automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.00,0:28:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.04,0:29:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. It's my first time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.04,0:29:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I flew all the way from Poland.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.04,0:29:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt a very strong magnetic pull to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.04,0:29:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I understand from one point of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.04,0:29:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a lot of questions that I could ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.04,0:29:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but then I don't really have any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.04,0:29:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just wanted to thank you so much, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.04,0:29:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Thank you very much, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.04,0:29:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.04,0:29:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,From Warsaw. Warsaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.04,0:29:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been in Poland.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.04,0:29:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.40,0:29:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where I grew up, wonky.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.40,0:29:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They brought part of Poland over and planted it in Milwaukee, Wisconsin.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.78,0:29:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Polish sausage.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.78,0:29:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I love Polish everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.78,0:29:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Polish weddings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.78,0:29:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Polish weddings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.78,0:29:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.78,0:29:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone for four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.78,0:29:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus for four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.78,0:29:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Four days?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.78,0:29:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.78,0:29:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.78,0:29:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.78,0:29:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Thank you, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.78,0:29:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.78,0:29:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thank you for coming from Poland.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.78,0:30:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.09,0:30:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.09,0:30:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.64,0:30:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.34,0:30:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I can just read your book and video for my work?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.38,0:30:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do I still need to find a spiritual teacher to guide me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.70,0:30:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.70,0:30:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can she just read our books and look at our videos?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.70,0:30:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should she find a spiritual teacher to guide her also?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.70,0:30:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think she ought to just study first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.99,0:30:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually the first steps is to study and become familiar with the vocabulary and the concepts.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.15,0:30:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And because you wouldn't know what teacher to pick, I would first be a student and learn
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.21,0:30:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,what you can about spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.21,0:30:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And the various spiritual pathways, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.47,0:30:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First, learn all you can learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.63,0:30:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they say when the student is ready, the teacher appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.63,0:31:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's too early to pick out a teacher at this level, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.43,0:31:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.25,0:31:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.25,0:31:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.67,0:31:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping you can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.88,0:31:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a bit of a dilemma, actually, which I'm hoping you could solve for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.88,0:31:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've got to give you—
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.88,0:31:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.88,0:31:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Too close?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.88,0:31:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.88,0:31:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I listen to your videos and everyone's too far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.88,0:31:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I come up here—
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.88,0:31:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.88,0:31:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.88,0:31:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyways, I've read all of your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.20,0:31:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're phenomenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.20,0:31:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the process of trying to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.20,0:31:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I don't have a say in that, but there's continually surrendering and getting below
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.20,0:31:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the thoughts and not thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.20,0:31:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, I have some studying requirements.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.20,0:31:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the process of doing a thesis, which in my mind requires studying and basically
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.20,0:31:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,reloading the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.20,0:31:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.20,0:31:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.20,0:31:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.20,0:31:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.20,0:31:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.20,0:31:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.20,0:31:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.20,0:31:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.20,0:31:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.20,0:32:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do that, and I was wondering if you could give me some advice on how to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.59,0:32:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,basically balance those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.59,0:32:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are two different tasks with two different goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.38,0:32:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The writing, you say you're doing writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.38,0:32:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a thesis, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.09,0:32:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.09,0:32:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing a thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.09,0:32:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.09,0:32:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm study—
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.09,0:32:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So the intention of the thesis is academic?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.98,0:32:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.98,0:32:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.68,0:32:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what is the other thing you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.86,0:32:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Setting the spiritual reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.95,0:32:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.42,0:32:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.61,0:32:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Two different processes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.68,0:32:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought they were sort of conflicting in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.01,0:32:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're just two different levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.85,0:32:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.77,0:32:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the intellectual is in the 400s
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.77,0:32:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and the spiritual is 500 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.85,0:32:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay, well I knew that, but.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.31,0:32:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so you can be both at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.98,0:32:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.90,0:32:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be smart, educated, and also holy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.79,0:33:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess right now, one out of three isn't bad, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.55,0:33:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now people often wonder, is there a conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.57,0:33:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,between the spiritual and intellectual?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.72,0:33:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason is supposed to reinforce faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.86,0:33:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith is supposed to illuminate reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.08,0:33:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.93,0:33:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm interested in choosing a career path
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.43,0:33:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and earlier you touched on the subject
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.76,0:33:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of whether or not a job, you know, is this a good job?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.63,0:33:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.47,0:33:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you talked about being precise and do good in what way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.67,0:33:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering if it would be an appropriate question
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.23,0:33:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask whether or not, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.32,0:33:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to make a list of possible career choices and then ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.43,0:33:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.86,0:33:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If the list, if the one was on the list, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.34,0:33:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the one that was the most, that best used my talents
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.78,0:33:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and that served the highest good,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.34,0:33:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,would that be an appropriate question to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.02,0:33:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course, and you can use kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.78,0:34:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at your area.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.86,0:34:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,interest and then
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.97,0:34:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you can ask which would be the best
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.78,0:34:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,pathway for you at this time in your life
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.65,0:34:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,which may be different than at a later time
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.57,0:34:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'd say at this time
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.17,0:34:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in my life it would be
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.61,0:34:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,most advantageous to follow
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.42,0:34:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you can pick which ones seem to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.26,0:34:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,stand out to you as meaningful
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.96,0:34:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.13,0:34:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.11,0:34:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,would you sign this please
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.90,0:34:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,my question is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.36,0:34:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to teach my children right from wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.67,0:34:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.32,0:34:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with that sometimes you go into
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.40,0:34:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,positionality and judgmentalism
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.00,0:34:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so I want them
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.36,0:34:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to know which things
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.96,0:34:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,are good and which things are not
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.48,0:34:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but not to then go and say
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.92,0:34:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,oh that's bad
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.80,0:34:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you see what I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.61,0:35:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it feels like a little bit of a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.34,0:35:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.59,0:35:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you want to teach them right from wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.17,0:35:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't want them to get into calling things wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.67,0:35:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and at the same time you're teaching them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.07,0:35:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,right from wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.23,0:35:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,right from wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.26,0:35:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,right from wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.80,0:35:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.42,0:35:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.88,0:35:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,how about good and not so good
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.36,0:35:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,some things are good
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.98,0:35:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,than others
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.67,0:35:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah I feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.73,0:35:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,society sends lots of really wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.03,0:35:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,messages through the media
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.23,0:35:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and just examples you see
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.30,0:35:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so I feel a real strong need
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.01,0:35:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to counteract that and to be
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.94,0:35:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,strong with
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.40,0:35:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what I tell them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.44,0:35:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,there again comes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.84,0:35:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,duality
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.19,0:35:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,positionality
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.76,0:35:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and judgmentalism
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.92,0:35:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're labeling it right and wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.71,0:35:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,or good or bad
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.65,0:35:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's still
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.51,0:35:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,either way you do it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.57,0:35:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it's still right and wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.90,0:35:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and good or bad
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.76,0:35:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.67,0:35:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not influencing them by telling them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.09,0:35:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,this is good and this is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.98,0:35:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not influencing them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.21,0:35:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I sometimes see them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.57,0:35:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,being judgmental a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.17,0:35:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,then they need to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.98,0:36:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then it depends on what they're judgmental about
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.26,0:36:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if they decide they're not going to watch this program
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.44,0:36:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that's good
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.84,0:36:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,especially if it has nudity in it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.71,0:36:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but if they're watching cartoons and there's violence
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.71,0:36:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to a place where I'm trying to be
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.07,0:36:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,like sometimes I'll say to them
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.80,0:36:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll say look at that mom
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.63,0:36:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll say yeah but that's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.90,0:36:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because they can do that if they want to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.92,0:36:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it's okay for them to be that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.36,0:36:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but isn't that what they are
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.28,0:36:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean isn't that all they are
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.80,0:36:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we as parents have to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.40,0:36:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,set the boundaries for our children
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.96,0:36:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to be clear
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.51,0:36:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,behavioral boundaries
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.71,0:36:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,forget about being judgmental
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.53,0:36:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,forget about being judgmental
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.57,0:36:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you better be judgmental
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.07,0:36:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but as an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.76,0:36:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and a spiritual student
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.28,0:36:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to work towards that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.44,0:36:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they have to have the basics first
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.71,0:36:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so forget about it when you're a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.05,0:36:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,forget about post graduate school
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.98,0:37:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're still getting through grade school
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.53,0:37:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,they gotta know right from wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.05,0:37:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.34,0:37:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what we have jails for
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.75,0:37:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we were never taught right from wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.17,0:37:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,just
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.80,0:37:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,want them to be tolerant
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.96,0:37:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and compassionate
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.73,0:37:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,wait until they're older
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.00,0:37:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,well it's also right or wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.59,0:37:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,regarding your own behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.88,0:37:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or behavior of others
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.19,0:37:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.30,0:37:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no qualms
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.26,0:37:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,hi Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.90,0:37:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just like to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.05,0:37:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.94,0:37:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything that you are
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.53,0:37:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just wanted to come here
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.46,0:37:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to see if I could get your blessing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.65,0:37:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,on the spiritual path
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.67,0:37:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you on the spiritual path
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.61,0:37:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,amen
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.94,0:37:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you sir
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.76,0:37:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,hello
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.57,0:37:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,may I shake your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.57,0:37:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.30,0:37:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much for all of your work
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.90,0:38:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,my question has to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.00,0:38:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.69,0:38:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,when I have some interactions
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.82,0:38:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,with other individuals
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.13,0:38:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.55,0:38:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,occasionally I have some
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.76,0:38:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughts which arise
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.71,0:38:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,which are unbidden
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.90,0:38:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and are totally inappropriate
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.57,0:38:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,for the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.84,0:38:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you mean appropriate
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.48,0:38:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,socially
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.92,0:38:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,expressed or internally
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.30,0:38:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,unsound expressed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.40,0:38:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,internally unexpressed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.67,0:38:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and why do you call it inappropriate
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.13,0:38:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.25,0:38:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.17,0:38:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,well yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.69,0:38:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the other part is
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.46,0:38:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is that occasionally
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.78,0:38:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,there have been times
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.03,0:38:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when I've actually acted out
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.09,0:38:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,on those thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.94,0:38:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.26,0:38:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.73,0:38:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,if you might have some insight
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.07,0:38:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,into that because
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.96,0:38:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,no because I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.53,0:38:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,whether they're correct thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.65,0:38:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,or incorrect thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.17,0:38:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,or whether they're sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.17,0:38:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,psychotic thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.28,0:39:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean what kind of thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.17,0:39:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,are you talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.05,0:39:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,well it's situationally inappropriate
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.13,0:39:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for example I might
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.57,0:39:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,be talking to somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.69,0:39:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know I might say
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.15,0:39:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to myself internally
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.90,0:39:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,a thought completely unbidden
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.71,0:39:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,would arise
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.44,0:39:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,would say
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.65,0:39:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of an example here
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.67,0:39:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,um
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.21,0:39:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,this guy's an idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.96,0:39:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you're thinking of
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.94,0:39:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,well sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.65,0:39:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.55,0:39:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,this might be like an idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.73,0:39:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and what is your question
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.76,0:39:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is it okay to say it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.13,0:39:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.88,0:39:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.11,0:39:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.63,0:39:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,no right
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.19,0:39:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,spend your life in court
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.03,0:39:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,right right
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.13,0:39:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess that's
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.76,0:39:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,now we learn how to screen our impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.34,0:39:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and screen our thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.57,0:39:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,well I guess you know
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.94,0:39:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm having a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.55,0:39:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,slight realization
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.82,0:39:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,about this
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.57,0:39:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.07,0:40:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,could it be narcissism
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.32,0:40:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that would want me to
