Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.82,0:51:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to the way I wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.82,0:51:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what she's asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.03,0:51:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a method that she's been involved with
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.03,0:51:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and she wants to know if she should continue
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.03,0:51:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,practicing this method.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.03,0:51:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worthwhile going for it or should I drop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.03,0:51:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do you feel a benefit from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.03,0:51:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.03,0:51:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you asking the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.03,0:51:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it does not evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.03,0:51:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not find students who want to learn it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.03,0:51:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and it does not evolve the way I would like
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.03,0:51:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in relation to the effort which I put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.03,0:51:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just think it might be a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.03,0:51:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. You're making a...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.03,0:51:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.63,0:51:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what the question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.63,0:51:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a method and it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.63,0:51:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is your complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.17,0:52:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like more people to benefit from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.17,0:52:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to inflict your will upon them
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.17,0:52:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and get them to do the same thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.17,0:52:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.86,0:52:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to sign them up for something
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.86,0:52:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that you find favorable and beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.86,0:52:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And although that may be a good thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.86,0:52:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not 100% pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.86,0:52:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.59,0:52:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.65,0:52:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You have mixed goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.65,0:52:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mixed goals, seeing and mixing goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.65,0:52:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.90,0:52:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.76,0:52:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.73,0:52:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.21,0:52:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.21,0:52:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.67,0:52:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask that some more people are here
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.67,0:53:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,who actually follow this teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.67,0:53:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and my question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.67,0:53:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is that he made a decision today
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.67,0:53:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for one of my friends who's in this school
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.67,0:53:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to not come back because...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.05,0:53:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. Tell me what he said so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.05,0:53:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He said a friend of his made a decision not to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.09,0:53:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back where?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.09,0:53:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.09,0:53:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This spiritual teacher we are following.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.75,0:53:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual teacher they're following.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.75,0:53:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who we are following?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.75,0:53:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who they are following.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.75,0:53:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.75,0:53:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You and somebody else are following some spiritual teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.75,0:53:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.75,0:53:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the question now?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.75,0:53:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And he made the decision that he was not...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.75,0:53:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't want to come back to that school.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.75,0:53:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The friend of his decided to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.75,0:53:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.75,0:53:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know if his decision was based on truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.75,0:53:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,just based on his...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.75,0:53:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.75,0:54:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all spiritual teachers are for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.73,0:54:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.73,0:54:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to know if his decision not to come back
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.73,0:54:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,was or not to...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.73,0:54:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not allowed to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.73,0:54:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not allowed to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.73,0:54:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To his teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.73,0:54:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To this particular teaching, if that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.73,0:54:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.73,0:54:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he, stealing money from poor children or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.73,0:54:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not allowed to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.73,0:54:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's following a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.73,0:54:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You and him are both following this...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.73,0:54:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.73,0:54:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.73,0:54:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he got through his own mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.94,0:54:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he said that by coming here,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.94,0:54:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we are interfering with his direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.01,0:54:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he didn't say it in these words.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.90,0:54:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't say it in these words.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.90,0:54:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,By your group coming here or...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.90,0:54:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.90,0:54:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That you were interfering with his direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.90,0:54:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't interfere with anyone's direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.90,0:54:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I come up here because I would like to ask it for all of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.75,0:55:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but I actually don't know how to ask the question correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.75,0:55:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.75,0:55:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.75,0:55:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.76,0:55:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They are...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.53,0:55:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They are all following a certain spiritual teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.53,0:55:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is they?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.53,0:55:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This group that has come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.53,0:55:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's a whole group here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.53,0:55:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.53,0:55:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.53,0:55:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And they are all...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.53,0:55:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, where are they from?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.53,0:55:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.55,0:55:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Holland.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.55,0:55:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.71,0:55:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this teaching is all over the world, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.71,0:55:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.71,0:55:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, they are most...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.71,0:55:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They live in California.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.71,0:55:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.71,0:55:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I live in Holland right now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.71,0:55:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.71,0:55:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.71,0:55:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't get what is the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.71,0:55:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're saying this...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.71,0:55:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This particular teacher is saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.71,0:55:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.71,0:56:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That coming here would interfere with their pathway that he has them on, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.71,0:56:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a threat to the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.71,0:56:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.71,0:56:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.71,0:56:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What pathway, inasmuch as we don't have any particular pathway,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.42,0:56:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,how did this interfere?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.42,0:56:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you just calibrate what's the level of the highest truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.42,0:56:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and you follow the highest truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.42,0:56:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that interfere?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.42,0:56:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that interfere?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.42,0:56:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.32,0:56:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it interferes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.32,0:56:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.05,0:56:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.05,0:56:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It puts...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.05,0:56:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Some spiritual teacher's nose is out of joint,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.05,0:56:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,when he heard that they were coming to hear these lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.05,0:56:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For one thing, we calibrate the level of consciousness of all the teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.05,0:56:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's a number of teachers that are not at all pleased by that problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.05,0:56:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that problem that creates.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.05,0:56:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Some are not even at 200, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.05,0:56:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.05,0:56:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.05,0:56:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.05,0:56:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.05,0:56:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.05,0:56:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.05,0:56:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.05,0:56:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.05,0:56:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.05,0:56:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.05,0:56:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.05,0:56:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.05,0:56:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.05,0:56:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.05,0:56:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.15,0:56:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That problem that creates.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.38,0:57:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Some are not even at 200, you see what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.23,0:57:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They have many followers, so that doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.55,0:57:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I was a teacher whose integrity was in doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.40,0:57:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want you running here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.67,0:57:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is you learn how to calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.42,0:57:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You calibrate the level of the teacher and then have it affirmed by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.67,0:57:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.67,0:57:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's how you fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.26,0:57:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.26,0:57:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what this teacher's fearing, that we're going to calibrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.26,0:57:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not worried about the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.92,0:57:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's his problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.92,0:57:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,about the students. It's the students that hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.86,0:57:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,not the teacher. You're
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.28,0:57:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,responsible for your own spiritual destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.17,0:57:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.01,0:57:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,going to appear and speak
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.09,0:57:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in your behalf before the Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.38,0:57:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.65,0:58:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this teacher speak for you
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.67,0:58:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,before Almighty God
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.94,0:58:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have led them in this direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.34,0:58:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O Lord? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.36,0:58:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do you want with a teacher like that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.09,0:58:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,who won't eat the bread that he bakes
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.88,0:58:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,himself? If you
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.34,0:58:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,won't eat the bread that you bake yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.61,0:58:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you shouldn't be a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.53,0:58:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.26,0:58:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ promises to be
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.03,0:58:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,before the Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.92,0:58:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be your what? Blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.42,0:58:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Advocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.11,0:58:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.51,0:58:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a spiritual teacher must
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.86,0:58:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,be responsible and
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.86,0:58:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,be willing to appear before God
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.78,0:58:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and take the responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.15,0:58:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have taught them this
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.82,0:58:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,out of my best intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.82,0:58:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I am incorrect, I pray
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.88,0:58:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.01,0:58:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,For forgiveness, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.84,0:59:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to take responsibility as a
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.96,0:59:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,teacher. So never follow
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.17,0:59:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a teacher who doesn't take responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.71,0:59:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,accountability for what
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.21,0:59:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you have taught. So we could
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.65,0:59:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in a sense calibrate his intention
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.71,0:59:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with this decision this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.94,0:59:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what I would say, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.88,0:59:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate it amongst yourselves until you're
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.84,0:59:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,satisfied and understand
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.48,0:59:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,why you're getting that kind of a reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.94,0:59:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.67,0:59:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I can see the dilemma
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.48,0:59:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,now. Okay. Right. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.09,0:59:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. My question
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.09,0:59:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't nearly as deep as everybody else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.26,0:59:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.09,0:59:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,wondering if it was possible
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.55,0:59:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to calibrate the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.09,0:59:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,level of consciousness of the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.05,0:59:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,two presidential candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.84,1:00:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.30,1:00:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who the presidential
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.61,1:00:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,candidates are.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.19,1:00:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.13,1:00:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One is a wrinkled old man.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.09,1:00:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,White hair. Conservative.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.84,1:00:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A veteran of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.86,1:00:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Vietnam War.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.28,1:00:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a prisoner of war. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.48,1:00:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And was severely injured
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.90,1:00:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and tortured. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.57,1:00:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So the principles that he chose
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.38,1:00:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to live by seemed
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.34,1:00:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to be profoundly important
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.88,1:00:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because they were done for their own
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.71,1:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,sake, not because of some gain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.63,1:00:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So he didn't say, I choose to live by
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.67,1:00:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,this and believe in this because
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.53,1:00:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,by doing that, I
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.51,1:00:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,would then become president of XYZ
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.44,1:00:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Company. There was no gain
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.59,1:00:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.36,1:01:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So look to see what gain
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.15,1:01:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there is by people's proclamations
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.32,1:01:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of what they say and they believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.88,1:01:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.94,1:01:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know how to use the muscle
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.94,1:01:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,testing that we use,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.01,1:01:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll find out very quickly which
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.07,1:01:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is above 200 and which is not above
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.26,1:01:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,200. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.07,1:01:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And advise people to use it on their own
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.84,1:01:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,because I don't want to be quoted.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.59,1:01:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And within 30 minutes, it's going to be
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.40,1:01:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.09,1:01:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't put that on my blog.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.80,1:01:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you leave it off your blog.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.90,1:01:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.30,1:01:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.21,1:01:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, you didn't say anything
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.23,1:01:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,about the other candidate.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.67,1:01:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.92,1:01:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.48,1:01:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about the Course
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.76,1:01:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.44,1:01:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing the Course in Miracles
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.88,1:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for about a year,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.76,1:02:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm only on lesson
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.92,1:02:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,230.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.86,1:02:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.92,1:02:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.25,1:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're just asking me if there is a lack
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.86,1:02:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of benefit if sometimes I don't do a lesson
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.36,1:02:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in a day or...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.36,1:02:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's natural.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.26,1:02:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You start out feeling very I must do one
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.07,1:02:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,every day, but then you find that some
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.55,1:02:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,lessons are more meaningful than others.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.42,1:02:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want to spend a couple of days
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.05,1:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,really absorbing that and really getting
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.63,1:02:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the total meaning of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.88,1:02:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.69,1:02:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, take your time.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.69,1:02:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.69,1:02:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, you know, you get stalled and you spend
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.28,1:02:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole week on one lesson and then others don't
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.82,1:02:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,seem to be as significant to your life and you move
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.59,1:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,back to one a day again.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.40,1:02:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Course is a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.01,1:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.32,1:02:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.32,1:03:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think the Course in Miracles is a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.90,1:03:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see nothing as it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.40,1:03:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see only the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.73,1:03:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.73,1:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's mind boggling.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.30,1:03:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of those things are so mind boggling.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.86,1:03:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.86,1:03:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.71,1:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We tracked people doing a Course in Miracles and we found by less than 90 or so, they had
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.17,1:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,transcended the susceptibility to be negatively influenced by negative stimuli.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.44,1:03:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They could look at fluorescent lights and they no longer went weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.69,1:03:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.69,1:03:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So there was a confirmable physiologic change.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.69,1:03:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.05,1:03:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.05,1:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about the will.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.05,1:03:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,From my understanding, the personal will calibrate as high as the personal level of will.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.55,1:03:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a personal level of consciousness and then there's a divine will.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.94,1:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, how do I discern subjectively the experience between both?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.63,1:04:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would there be a difference?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.63,1:04:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I somehow believe I can make a wrong choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.57,1:04:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can follow the wrong will.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.57,1:04:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're trying to decide what is aligned with the will of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.32,1:04:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.32,1:04:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.32,1:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.32,1:04:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd say the higher it calibrates, better.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.32,1:04:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.32,1:04:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.40,1:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.40,1:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.88,1:04:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.88,1:04:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,By using the technique that we use, the higher it calibrates, the closer it is aligned with
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.63,1:04:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the will of God as we speak of it abstractly.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.63,1:04:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.63,1:04:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot calibrate by myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.76,1:04:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried, but I didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.76,1:04:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.76,1:04:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have friends that know how to do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.76,1:04:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.76,1:04:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.76,1:04:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good golly.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.07,1:04:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.07,1:04:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your spiritual education, your spiritual education, what differentiates the two is whether you're
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.96,1:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,looking to a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.96,1:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For gain or not for gain, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.92,1:05:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual progress is progress, but it's not necessarily a gain, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.42,1:05:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.42,1:05:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gain means you project a desirability upon something within the world and then yearn
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.84,1:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for it, you know, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.42,1:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now spiritual goals are more non-linear, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.05,1:05:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,More non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.05,1:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.05,1:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.96,1:05:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you've got to have a goal that you want to accomplish, and you want to achieve
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.98,1:05:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.98,1:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want to be the most loving that you can be towards all of life and all its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.98,1:05:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's enough for a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.88,1:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.88,1:05:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll keep you busy for a decade or two.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.88,1:05:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even those that don't deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.88,1:05:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even those that don't deserve it, that's a funny one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.42,1:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgive them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.42,1:05:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the ones who don't deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.63,1:05:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.63,1:05:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to give you a couple of examples.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.63,1:05:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.88,1:05:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.88,1:06:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah I just wanted to thank you and ask for your blessing yes and I also been
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.98,1:06:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to practice the being like kindness and lovingness to all things
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.73,1:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and all people in my daily life yes routine and I guess I found myself
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.96,1:06:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,people-pleasing a lot in a way that is oh yeah maybe I'll be I'll be with
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.94,1:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody and trying to just be kind and see the essence and innocence and love
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.80,1:06:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it and at the same time when I'm they're not receptive to that I will become
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.44,1:06:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,uncomfortable and become I'll purposely drop to a lower level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.55,1:06:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah I'm comfortable and then I stay in that level and feel shame about it and
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.30,1:06:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you had any advice well you do do a spiritual practice for its
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.17,1:06:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,own sake not because of the consequences
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.96,1:07:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,not because of the payoff do it for its own sake if God says you would love
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.23,1:07:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that's green you just love everything that's green you don't look
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.65,1:07:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for consequences okay so I wouldn't look for some kind of a significance or
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.65,1:07:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,consequence or an additional meaning you do a thing for its own sake because it's
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.90,1:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a basic spiritual dictum yeah and so if I am with somebody and I get a negative
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.26,1:07:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,response from being to to being there with them and loving who they are stay
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.63,1:07:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,with it stay with that state of being instead of accommodating a different
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.98,1:07:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,intent from them I don't get the question and so it's being loving
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.23,1:07:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,towards somebody and now he's becoming no he gets judgmental about it but what
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.90,1:07:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,if that person doesn't what respond yeah you know you can't look for a response
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.57,1:08:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah they have no no you're just loving towards the little toad because he's a
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.03,1:08:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,there and the toad
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.34,1:08:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,he's not going to kiss you you know
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.13,1:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,kiss a toad
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.00,1:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we got little toads behind our house
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.90,1:08:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we just go out and
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.05,1:08:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,love them but they still are toads
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.42,1:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't pick them up because you might get warts
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.90,1:08:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you can play with
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.71,1:08:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,life through your child you know
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.47,1:08:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody thinks they've got to be
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.98,1:08:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so serious about everything
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.22,1:08:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you know life is entertaining
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.43,1:08:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,hilarious
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.98,1:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you need to
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.17,1:08:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,people need to get their child
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.14,1:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,up and going you know the child
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.98,1:08:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,naively innocently just has
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.22,1:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a fun time with life
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.72,1:08:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we get the old
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.46,1:08:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,grandpa in us
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.34,1:09:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,get more into your child
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.89,1:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the child
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.40,1:09:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the child has a certain joie de vivre
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.80,1:09:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.38,1:09:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.38,1:09:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.46,1:09:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.47,1:09:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just wanted to spend a moment with you
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.77,1:09:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.31,1:09:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,a momento
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.19,1:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.72,1:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.34,1:09:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make it quick
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.88,1:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to come up and say thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.27,1:09:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,personally for the work
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.31,1:09:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and the wisdom that you put into the world
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.69,1:09:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for your thanks
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.77,1:09:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for your feedback
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.93,1:09:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and appreciation
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.81,1:10:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,hello
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.14,1:10:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.22,1:10:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have a
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.47,1:10:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,moment to simply sit here
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.52,1:10:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in silence with the both of you
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.31,1:10:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.06,1:10:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with all this blessed company here today
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.28,1:10:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the silence is always present
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.18,1:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,don't be confused by the sounds
