Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.75,1:16:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,oil
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.75,1:16:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as a show earlier, something like 6%.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.06,1:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And would it help to, there was an exercise
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.69,1:16:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and described in one of the books
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.27,1:16:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,where you listed all sorts of different problems
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.11,1:16:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and then boil it down, you, I guess, meditated over it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.14,1:16:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and boiled it down to, for example,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.65,1:16:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,overpopulation caused all these different various problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.10,1:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that help in any sort of analysis,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.11,1:16:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,like these economic problems?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.19,1:16:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it help?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.96,1:16:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, overpopulation is the cause
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.11,1:16:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of all the world's problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.35,1:16:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The price of oil, riots here and there, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.47,1:16:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I mean, a productive population
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.25,1:16:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is self-supporting and not a burden to others, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.01,1:16:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And it supports freedom and integrity and industry
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.22,1:17:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the things that the United States stands for,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.44,1:17:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and at least in theory.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.13,1:17:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.38,1:17:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.02,1:17:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.68,1:17:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time here,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.02,1:17:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel such a great blessing to be in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.96,1:17:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And today, I had a question, but today at lunch,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.77,1:17:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I talked with my boyfriend up in Bend, Oregon,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.69,1:17:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,who had a question, so I deferred to his question.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.00,1:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And his question is a curiosity of research indicates
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.76,1:17:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that dreaming is a result of,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.23,1:17:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,stress and having to resolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.43,1:17:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, dreaming is what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.22,1:17:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Research indicates that what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.84,1:17:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.68,1:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.00,1:17:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Resolves the stresses of the day
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.19,1:17:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,or conflicts that a person may have.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.61,1:17:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,His question was, over.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.11,1:18:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't make a broad blanket comment like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.68,1:18:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.52,1:18:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It sometimes does, depending on the person,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.57,1:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,depending on your intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.06,1:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You will sometimes find a dream clarifies
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.00,1:18:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,just as often as it does not.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.55,1:18:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,His question was, over.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.09,1:18:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Decalibrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.93,1:18:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Decalibrated level of 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.86,1:18:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.42,1:18:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Does one need to dream after one attains enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.89,1:18:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the body or the mind still produce dreaming state?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.32,1:18:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is sleeping just flat stillness?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.25,1:18:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.84,1:18:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anyone in the 600s,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.23,1:18:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,do they still have a dream state when sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.17,1:18:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.75,1:18:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know of any that do.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.02,1:18:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.31,1:18:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't asked anybody over 600 if they still dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.31,1:18:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they still dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.88,1:19:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.56,1:19:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams are few and far between the more advanced you get.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.53,1:19:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They do disappear, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.53,1:19:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.19,1:19:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They do disappear.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.53,1:19:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I think that would answer his question.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.84,1:19:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's a vignette of a thought form.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.68,1:19:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really your dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.43,1:19:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a thought form you picked up while you're out of body
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.14,1:19:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and floating around in the astral circus.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.43,1:19:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.97,1:19:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just as recognized in the sleep state then?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.97,1:19:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's recognized in the sleep state.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.84,1:19:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought form that you picked up?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.65,1:19:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, you may become more of a passing thought form,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.47,1:19:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,especially right before sleep, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.53,1:19:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypnagogic hallucinations occur there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.47,1:19:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypnagogic hallucinations, you're half awake and half asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.61,1:19:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the sensor, the sensor is, the guard is not up yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.11,1:19:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a brief moment there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.06,1:20:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called hypnagogic state, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.39,1:20:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Half asleep, half awake.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.19,1:20:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, and may I please shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.17,1:20:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.51,1:20:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And tell you thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.27,1:20:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.10,1:20:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my joy, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.02,1:20:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have what?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.69,1:20:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.10,1:20:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.92,1:20:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to try to talk very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.97,1:20:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I'd like to ask you if I may send your greetings
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.47,1:20:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and your blessings to Penny and Coco.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.25,1:20:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.75,1:20:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.31,1:20:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.55,1:20:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Two gorillas.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.21,1:20:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco's the gorilla and Penny's the human scientist
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.63,1:20:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that is owned by Coco.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.39,1:20:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Penny's is the scientist.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.82,1:21:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.32,1:21:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And Coco's the gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.67,1:21:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.38,1:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I certainly would be happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.93,1:21:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, we've calibrated Coco and Coco is higher
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.96,1:21:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,than a large percentage of the human population.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.02,1:21:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.85,1:21:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I heard about you because Penny
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.72,1:21:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and her sister Jenny knew about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.65,1:21:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And that Coco is in the book, so I'm very delighted
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.89,1:21:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to have the opportunity to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.39,1:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Coco is the consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.23,1:21:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco is, I remember correctly, what is Coco's caliber?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.07,1:21:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Something.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.82,1:21:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.47,1:21:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,405.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.47,1:21:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Coco understands.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.47,1:21:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Coco really understands.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.09,1:21:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Understands and does by sign language.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.60,1:21:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.52,1:21:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And what I thought was when he said sweet, soft kitty,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.31,1:21:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,good, good kitty, I just went, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.40,1:21:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but not all the kitties are good.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.40,1:21:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all the kitties are good kitties.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.10,1:21:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I, every time I talk to Penny,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.35,1:21:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask her to tell me a Coco story.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.89,1:22:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know you're short on time.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.31,1:22:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I share with her?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.05,1:22:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.81,1:22:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was talking to Penny and I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.64,1:22:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so tell me a Coco story.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.55,1:22:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And she said, oh, well, just two days ago, a couple of days ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.72,1:22:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was late coming back from lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.97,1:22:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knew I needed to get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.32,1:22:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And she said, so when she got back, she went directly to Coco.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.63,1:22:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And Coco picked up a sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.40,1:22:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And she picked up a sign out of a stack of signs that she had.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.35,1:22:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And the one she picked up and showed Penny was, I worried.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.14,1:22:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.05,1:22:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So to me, that meant that she could sort
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.55,1:22:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,through English language written in a stack of papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.13,1:22:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She could read.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.32,1:22:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I worried.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.32,1:22:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And that she could understand her emotions probably better
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.82,1:22:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,than what some of us can sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.17,1:22:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she picks up the emotion of that statement.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.97,1:22:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And was able to convey it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.27,1:22:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.21,1:22:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I just love Coco stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.21,1:22:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.21,1:22:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just love Coco.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.98,1:22:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.98,1:22:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm thrilled that she brought me to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.64,1:23:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.14,1:23:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Coco.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.14,1:23:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I do have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.14,1:23:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was going to try to make it very generic and quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.22,1:23:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.32,1:23:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll still try to talk fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.63,1:23:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a huge dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.67,1:23:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, there were eight hurricanes in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.47,1:23:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer have a house.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.89,1:23:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight hurricanes in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.28,1:23:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.28,1:23:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight hurricanes in 14 months.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.27,1:23:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer have a house or a home.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.60,1:23:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have six storage units of dresses and things.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.75,1:23:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to find a place to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.21,1:23:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a home.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.85,1:23:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I try to live my feet on the path
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.78,1:23:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and follow the highest and greatest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.35,1:23:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And so for three years, I've been
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.89,1:23:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,having wonderful opportunities to be with people
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.43,1:23:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and contribute not only to my highest and greatest good,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.67,1:23:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but to theirs.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.89,1:23:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.27,1:23:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a home.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.10,1:23:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to find a place to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.40,1:24:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time, it seems as if I ask guides and guardian angels,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.10,1:24:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have more than one.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.10,1:24:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And they don't all agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.71,1:24:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I get pulled in half a dozen different directions.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.25,1:24:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So is there a better method of finger testing or what help?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.18,1:24:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried pendulums.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.32,1:24:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't always give me the same answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.39,1:24:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the highest good, you want to know
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.82,1:24:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what's for your highest good?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.06,1:24:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where I can go that it will be for the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.93,1:24:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just go where you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.28,1:24:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I tried that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.22,1:24:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I went.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.27,1:24:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.60,1:24:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to Tennessee, to Nashville.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.27,1:24:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, OK, I'm tired of trying
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.81,1:24:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to follow the path of listening for the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.55,1:24:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to move to Nashville.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.05,1:24:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to make it work.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.21,1:24:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And this will be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.35,1:24:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It fell through very badly in very many ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.14,1:24:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was expensive and a disaster to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.78,1:24:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.28,1:24:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided, OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.98,1:24:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nashville, Tennessee?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.94,1:24:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.25,1:24:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't advise that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.14,1:24:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.64,1:24:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.17,1:24:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.98,1:24:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So now I'm back to following the path.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.98,1:24:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know, if my guardian angels
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.18,1:24:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,are arguing about, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.59,1:24:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Try Prescott.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.06,1:25:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you think arm testing?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.76,1:25:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of down to two places of Sedona or Florida, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.05,1:25:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.14,1:25:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Flora, you want to live where the hurricanes are?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.25,1:25:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really, which is why I'm not
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.98,1:25:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,taking a job in the Grand Cayman Islands,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.85,1:25:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,even though I really need a job, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.60,1:25:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Cayman.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.68,1:25:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right in the path.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.18,1:25:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.14,1:25:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, hurricanes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.76,1:25:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.42,1:25:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And they must have a lot of jobs.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.69,1:25:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of jobs available in that area.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.50,1:25:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the same reason they have them
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.18,1:25:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in the salt mines in Russia, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.68,1:25:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.18,1:25:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want that either.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.18,1:25:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No pretty clothes there.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.18,1:25:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So arm testing, muscle testing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.18,1:25:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.18,1:25:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A location.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.76,1:25:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just not getting an easy, direct path to a location.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.11,1:25:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I need to be in one place.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.56,1:25:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've now been four months in Cave Creek.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.38,1:25:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're asking an impossible question.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.97,1:25:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question you're asking?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.93,1:26:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I determine that a place is not a white hole mine?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.38,1:26:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.06,1:26:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask what is for your highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.14,1:26:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.77,1:26:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Period.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.81,1:26:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.72,1:26:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me the rest of the story.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.61,1:26:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.34,1:26:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Serve your highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.22,1:26:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.88,1:26:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And expect my feet to take me there?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.22,1:26:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do I have to throw a dart at a map?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.11,1:26:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.72,1:26:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for three years.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.18,1:26:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you said you came down to two places you'd like to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.68,1:26:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You said two places?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.97,1:26:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.48,1:26:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's your problem about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.06,1:26:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.72,1:26:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't determine whether it's, again, another Nashville.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.67,1:26:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's of my own mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.98,1:26:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it's the highest and greatest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.90,1:26:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever asked if it's the highest?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.52,1:26:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's afraid to make a decision for fear it'll be a wrong one.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.75,1:26:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've made so many decisions in the last three years,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.52,1:26:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and none of them took.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.90,1:26:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.63,1:26:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.27,1:26:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just keep flipping, flopping around the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.82,1:26:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and nothing works wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.56,1:26:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever needs me most, when I finish
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.67,1:26:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,what I'm doing in that next moment,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.22,1:26:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that's who I go help next.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.51,1:26:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I need to help myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.14,1:27:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Be in one place so that I can do more.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.27,1:27:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the question now?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.76,1:27:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I make a decision for the highest and greatest good?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.27,1:27:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one is attractive?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.35,1:27:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to just pick one that you find attractive
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.00,1:27:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and that makes the arm go strong as an adequate place?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.06,1:27:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes my arm go strong, OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.00,1:27:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've not had anybody to do muscle testing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.23,1:27:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.15,1:27:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.06,1:27:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.65,1:27:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what people do.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.47,1:27:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asking about herself, so it's hard for her to make.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.26,1:27:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.50,1:27:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's of my mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.03,1:27:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And what does she mean by being happy?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.81,1:27:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she mean being fulfilled?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.65,1:27:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she mean becoming enriched?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.11,1:27:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she mean becoming educated?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.65,1:27:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she mean making wonderful relationships?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.89,1:27:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you want heaven on earth?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.26,1:27:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.93,1:27:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.53,1:27:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've got to wait to get to heaven on earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.31,1:27:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.81,1:27:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.31,1:27:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest and greatest good, and I really
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.07,1:27:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,do want to contribute.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.27,1:27:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to hold the two places in mind, first one
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.97,1:27:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the other?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.93,1:27:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.89,1:27:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.68,1:27:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do one.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.51,1:27:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.06,1:27:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to help her with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.75,1:28:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.25,1:28:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.15,1:28:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.65,1:28:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold the first one in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.35,1:28:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.35,1:28:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That location would serve her highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.88,1:28:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.32,1:28:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.82,1:28:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hold the other location in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.13,1:28:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.23,1:28:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That location would hold her highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.30,1:28:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.97,1:28:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Highest good is what you make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.39,1:28:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.89,1:28:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.39,1:28:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a location.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.53,1:28:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.19,1:28:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.69,1:28:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.46,1:28:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And blessings.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.19,1:28:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to send this photograph to Coco and Penny.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.96,1:28:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.76,1:28:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Send Coco my greetings.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.69,1:28:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.69,1:28:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.96,1:28:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco is beautiful and charming.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.81,1:28:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She is.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.76,1:28:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.26,1:28:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She wears pearls.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.98,1:28:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She likes pearls?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.05,1:28:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a pearl necklace, and she loves lacy curtains.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.55,1:28:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.46,1:28:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.64,1:28:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.90,1:28:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.78,1:28:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.44,1:28:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you for all your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.67,1:28:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.25,1:28:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And to let you know that you are my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.28,1:29:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.10,1:29:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.25,1:29:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.14,1:29:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Both places would be adequate.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.67,1:29:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.32,1:29:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.82,1:29:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.32,1:29:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.82,1:29:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.32,1:29:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.39,1:29:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like to be in your presence and hold your hand for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.01,1:29:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.51,1:29:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.38,1:29:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.19,1:29:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was wondering, a lot of my friends
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.56,1:29:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,are into this Anastasia thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.23,1:29:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you've heard of it, but I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.85,1:29:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anastasia thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.92,1:29:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that, a cookie or a?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.35,1:29:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.85,1:29:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.35,1:29:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So Anastasia is this lady who lives in the Russian taiga for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.35,1:29:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And she just lives this certain, like, natural life.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.57,1:29:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just wondering if she muscle tests above 200 or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.39,1:30:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is somebody who lives in Australia?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.47,1:30:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Russian taiga.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.72,1:30:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.22,1:30:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Russian.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.30,1:30:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.19,1:30:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.89,1:30:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.53,1:30:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.03,1:30:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.53,1:30:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this guy, Vladimir Smeagher,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.88,1:30:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,who writes books about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.50,1:30:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he's talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.72,1:30:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask if Anastasia muscle tests above 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.05,1:30:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know if that person who
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.90,1:30:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,claims to be the Princess Anastasia is actually
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.78,1:30:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the Princess Anastasia?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.75,1:30:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.25,1:30:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your question?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.94,1:30:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.44,1:30:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not a princess.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.56,1:30:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a lady who lives in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.44,1:30:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a lady whose name is Anastasia, who lives in Russia.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.82,1:30:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we want to know about her for?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.52,1:30:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because his friends are following her.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.75,1:30:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to know if she's above 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.13,1:30:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, as a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.89,1:30:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know if she's a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.05,1:30:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a naturalist.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.56,1:30:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A naturalist?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.60,1:30:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.85,1:30:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that we wanted to do a naturalist.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.68,1:30:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.07,1:30:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.00,1:30:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask one more question?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.75,1:30:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way that I can decide?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.97,1:31:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, decide if something, like without muscle testing,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.98,1:31:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if something that I want is for my highest good,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.59,1:31:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or if it's like a self-destructive ego?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.94,1:31:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can just ask through prayer, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.97,1:31:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Lord, I ask for a miracle, a confirmation of this choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.42,1:31:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.10,1:31:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it serves the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.85,1:31:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, very few people do muscle testing on the planet,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.47,1:31:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet they live complete lives, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.89,1:31:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So your intuition and your primary goals,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.57,1:31:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in life, what you want to achieve and accomplish, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.34,1:31:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So it isn't always just from an esoteric viewpoint,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.76,1:31:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but, you know, a more practical viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.73,1:31:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can just ask for it to be shown to me through prayer,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.85,1:31:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's for my highest good or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.73,1:31:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.02,1:31:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.52,1:31:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.31,1:32:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.14,1:32:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.84,1:32:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hopkins?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.34,1:32:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.64,1:32:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you so much for your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.60,1:32:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just discovered it about a year ago, and I've read all
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.42,1:32:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of your books now, and so I'm very excited to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.97,1:32:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.34,1:32:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I did have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.03,1:32:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In your book, you mentioned, you know, how rare it is to be enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.47,1:32:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and that at this time there are numerous people on our planet
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.52,1:32:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that are enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.00,1:32:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There are numerous people that are what?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.76,1:32:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That are enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.47,1:32:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you get that?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.30,1:32:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In your book, it said there were several people that calibrated above.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.02,1:32:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought that was several.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.43,1:32:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.73,1:32:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.42,1:32:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what she was referring to.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.46,1:32:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, there had only been maybe one at a time,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.22,1:32:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and now we have like 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.89,1:32:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think there's three, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.42,1:32:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.39,1:32:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That are way up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.38,1:32:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but anyway, what's the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.30,1:32:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that because there's so much information now that,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.14,1:33:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or more teachers available so that enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.73,1:33:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.85,1:33:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No? Why is it that there's so many now?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.07,1:33:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.97,1:33:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.55,1:33:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where our population is.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.78,1:33:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Our population is growing, so of course there's going to be more people
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.98,1:33:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to counter the balance of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.14,1:33:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's just ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.43,1:33:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.55,1:33:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Above 600, there are currently three, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.22,1:33:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, well, thank you very much, and thank you so much for your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.22,1:33:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, a group like this counterbalances, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.02,1:33:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,frankly the negativity of the rest of mankind, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.93,1:33:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, good afternoon to you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.97,1:33:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.02,1:33:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is in one of your books, you suggest that it's
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.56,1:33:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a good idea to try to find yourself in the map of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.42,1:33:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm having a lot of difficulty with that,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.60,1:33:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because I see myself on a lot of different levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.22,1:34:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't say you should find yourself on a level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.15,1:34:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You did, I would, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.80,1:34:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not say that anywhere in any book.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.97,1:34:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I, for some reason, that's what I thought you said.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.80,1:34:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.63,1:34:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.27,1:34:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,On the map, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.93,1:34:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't advise people to try and calibrate their own level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.44,1:34:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I discourage them.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.63,1:34:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're never going to get a correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.68,1:34:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay, because I thought it would be very helpful for me to see the project,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.89,1:34:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the things that I project out into the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.28,1:34:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you look at the scale of consciousness, and you pick out the description
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.44,1:34:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of how you experience the world, primarily, and how you see the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.21,1:34:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you feel your purpose in life is, and you'll settle out on it
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.44,1:34:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,without any numerical designation.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.02,1:34:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though for myself, at least, I see myself on sometimes below 200 and sometimes above.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.48,1:34:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't fluctuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.64,1:34:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the passing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.68,1:34:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a passing mood or a passing thought, but your life doesn't change that fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.06,1:34:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life doesn't change overnight, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.25,1:34:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do I ascertain something like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.44,1:35:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, how do I find that?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.93,1:35:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's start with what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.25,1:35:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to be a psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.18,1:35:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finishing my PhD.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.47,1:35:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're in the 400s already, correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.64,1:35:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.10,1:35:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're asking the question without studying it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.22,1:35:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, you know, mental, the intellectual is in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.53,1:35:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just go up, intellectual, mental, getting a PhD, you're automatically in the 400s, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.69,1:35:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I didn't know that, but since you say it, then I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.46,1:35:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, are you familiar with the scale of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.14,1:35:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.80,1:35:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.30,1:35:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then you're not thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.85,1:35:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.53,1:35:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't think.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.80,1:35:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For some of the things you say, that there's corresponding emotions that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.10,1:35:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the different column, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.22,1:35:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it also, it tells you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.38,1:35:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The 300s is integrity and empowerment, 400s is the intellect, 500s is love, 600s is enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.97,1:35:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It says right there on the page.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.38,1:36:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just think what it says on the page.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.38,1:36:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.38,1:36:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't know that it's that simple that you just find yourself and you're done.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.38,1:36:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.38,1:36:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.38,1:36:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.38,1:36:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you can just find yourself and you're done.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.38,1:36:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.38,1:36:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.38,1:36:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody works on PhD unless they're, you know, in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.38,1:36:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.38,1:36:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
