Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.38,1:36:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.38,1:36:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not working on their PhDs.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.38,1:36:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
